{"tid":94183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【北極圈淪陷】支那追極光　北歐、加拿大出團急增1倍","createTime":"2017-01-25T04:40:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-29T08:39:27.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f552ddf3e699bfe456556a4cf2947f24529e7857","tid":94183,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T04:40:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.v3wall.com/wallpaper/1680_1050/1212/1680_1050_20121207124718655682.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.v3wall.com%2Fwallpaper%2F1680_1050%2F1212%2F1680_1050_20121207124718655682.jpg&h=cde6dfba&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n農曆新年將至，不少廣州民眾都外出避年，今年新春旅行團多屬長線遊，美國、加拿大、澳洲、英國、新西蘭都是熱門路線，其中，不少旅行團都打着「太陽黑子爆發期」睇極光作招徠，往北歐、俄羅斯、加拿大等地的人數，比去年同期急增100%。<br />\n<br />\n廣東的旅遊業者指出，今年新春期間出境遊佔整體業務一半，航線增加令到往歐洲機票價格變得便宜，今年去歐洲的旅行團價格比往年平二至四成，新春期間英國、愛爾蘭12天團開價1.39萬元（人民幣．下同），比去年便宜9,900元。<br />\n<br />\n今年冬季出境遊的另一個焦點是太陽黑子爆發期，越來越多人都趁外遊期間欣賞極光的遊客，故俄羅斯、北歐、加拿大等地的參團人數急增。<br />\n<br />\n東南亞方面，泰國仍是出境遊人數最多的地點，除了傳統目的地以外，今年有旅行社用包機前往甲米島，吸引部份人再到泰國。"},{"pid":"ea9a4056c16c055aa693f167711bbcade2fe0dcd","tid":94183,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T12:55:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"965c0cd6223b9b0672ff4cb472aa09a440231d14","tid":94183,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T13:13:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd131b0ad4d982178aa430c2aa90d4bf4b4a7af6","tid":94183,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T18:13:55.000Z","msg":"極光都俾支那人污染啦好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係極光上面寫到此一遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c62a6aa4d1316d77e78fab023e1732c1759c6842","tid":94183,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T18:52:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dccd109b5a20c0c8a50647658285398233a566a9","tid":94183,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T02:23:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3769ec8b8e2fce90972ccc7cf8b24d6f6b259267","tid":94183,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T08:28:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ded8548f410ff44888d677ad83889aea1ff8e0f","tid":94183,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T08:33:00.000Z","msg":"oh...shit"},{"pid":"e0151426e3b08fb96fcc0a0f98bcf8eafb25bfba","tid":94183,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T08:34:29.000Z","msg":"去太陽感受啦<br />\n求下唔好污染北歐北美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"201ad353a32894786ad9ec89e83b2c31f7f73b91","tid":94183,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T10:04:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32f9563aa8dc11ca8dc09b67a42fa863a1f3e00a","tid":94183,"uid":7704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T10:07:19.000Z","msg":"我求佢地留返係自己國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a720d2565dbb37126e53bc42ca876007fcbc0432","tid":94183,"uid":1672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T10:10:31.000Z","msg":"又話鎖國既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61a884d318c441916a28e0965e8eb9303fa12a32","tid":94183,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T08:39:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}